BETTER known as a track runner, with a sub-four-minute mile and a national
1500m title to his credit, Adrian Callan proved his worth as a cross-country
runner with his first win in the senior six-mile race at the SAF Western
District Cross-country championships at Stepps beating clubmate Graeme Wight by
